Package game

Class OxygenDispenser

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.monash.fit2099.engine.Ground
      • game.OxygenDispenser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Printable, Skilled
    public class OxygenDispenser
extends Ground
    Class representing an oxygen dispenser of terrain type. Oxygen dispenser has a button that allow other actor to press to cause it to produce an oxygen tank in its location on the next turn. The button will only work when dispenser is not producing the tank and there is no oxygen tank in the location that has not been retrieved.
